{"tid":587510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Poly厹被起底後自爆 仲講到自己無錯 🤮","createTime":"2018-03-10T13:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T15:30:17.000Z","uid":169338,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12ede00ca94c2f6a46318c05a058a2986668ddf1","tid":587510,"uid":169338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T13:14:03.000Z","msg":"[多圖](poly) 釣釣下狗公 釣到好姊妹個男友 -第一集<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/544220/page/11?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/544220/page/11?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n[多圖](Poly) 釣釣下狗公 釣到好姊妹個男友-第二集<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/544907/page/8?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/544907/page/8?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n我忍唔住要回應啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啊樓豬你呢位<span style=\"color: red;\">紅巴</span> 大個仔啦唔好再做埋呢d無聊野想拆散我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n件事其實我一早一五一十同左女朋友講同埋認左錯 女朋友你見到呢個cm既話我想再講多次對唔住我唔會再搞三搞四同咁貪玩 巴絲為鑒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果連登仲有正義既話求你地唔好po我女朋友既相出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢係無辜 頭先仲同我講好驚<br />\n同埋我地依家好幸福 多得樓豬你係度搞事同騷擾我地先經歷咁多有依家咁sweet 多謝巴絲關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後一句送給樓豬：你好自為之啦。放心，我未可憐到要係個mon面前放番你d野出黎刷存在感⋯⋯負皮都懶得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 事主本人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/10/211354_44f795469ba4256f6d8db27843490f11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F10%2F211354_44f795469ba4256f6d8db27843490f11.png&h=f1690587&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d93b2afe5ebc4f3356ba65423bf84c79b526871c","tid":587510,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T13:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646e039a4ddb6f67ed1301bc26528a157bdbe59b","tid":587510,"uid":169338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963b19405a9a488065438653089e2e64b1428ac5","tid":587510,"uid":98317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母on 9仔<br />\n咁都po上連登"},{"pid":"1c5e61611838fc8e6bcef6cbecd92bc14f3ffc11","tid":587510,"uid":44854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"講到1999<br />\n事主本人即係你自己定果2個post既樓主呀？"},{"pid":"a4428c7a1fd5a9ae1c607cb721426efa01db9df0","tid":587510,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:20:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84ee5b9d531a0b9c29f86814b5b37773c4126f99","tid":587510,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7546c7d94d5c258c72cc066e13b08c5b695ae18","tid":587510,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:20:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84472f6b091adcfd999af1ed0ee1b3471eef8f1f","tid":587510,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:20:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46d35dc414086e45091724662305582f19e9e6ec","tid":587510,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:21:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4f318643c249f038eef8bb246e938b8c91f75e8","tid":587510,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:21:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"213a7ed4401d4c97d0736b43c092a5d015f61ee3","tid":587510,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"推